head(Kandidat)
## # A tibble: 6  15
##      r     S    RV    KF    CD    DR    SF   DKP    FK    DF   KRF     V    VS
##   <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl>

## 6  1984    56    10    42     8     0    21     0    NA    NA     4    20     5
## #  2 more variables: FP <dbl>, EL <dbl>
Kandidat_long <- Kandidat %>%
  pivot_longer(
    cols = -r, 
    names_to = "Parti",
    values_to = "Mandater")%>%
  filter(!is.na(Mandater)) 
vline_years <- c(1973, 1977, 1984, 1994, 2001)
partifarver <- c(
  "CD" = "#7D3F98",
  "DF" = "#FFD700",
  "DKP" = "#AE0030",
  "DR" = "#B0B0B0",
  "EL" = "#AE0030",
  "FK" = "#A67C52",
  "FP" = "#FF7F00",
  "KF" = "#1A932E",
  "KRF" = "#A67C52",
  "RV" = "#954FAD",
  "S" = "#E3000F",
  "SF" = "#C32026",
  "V" = "#00529F",
  "VS" = "#AE0030"
)
ggplot(Kandidat_long, aes(x = r, y = Mandater, color = Parti)) +
  geom_line(linewidth = 1) +
  scale_color_manual(values = partifarver)+
  geom_vline(xintercept = vline_years, color = "black", linetype = "dashed", size = 0.7) +
  geom_point() +
  theme_minimal() +
   theme_minimal()
## Warning: Using `size` aesthetic for lines was deprecated in ggplot2 3.4.0.

partifarver <- c(

  "DF" = "#FFD700",
  "DKP" = "#AE0030",
  "DR" = "#B0B0B0",
  "EL" = "#AE0030",
  "FK" = "#A67C52",
  "FP" = "#FF7F00",
  "KF" = "#1A932E",
  "KRF" = "#A67C52",
  "RV" = "#954FAD",
  "S" = "#E3000F",
  "SF" = "#C32026",
  "V" = "#00529F",
  "VS" = "#AE0030"
)
p <- ggplot(Kandidat_long, aes(x = r, y = Mandater, color = Parti)) +
  geom_line(linewidth = 1) +
  scale_color_manual(values = partifarver) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_vline(xintercept = vline_years, color = "black", linetype = "dashed", size = 0.7) +
  theme_minimal() +
  labs(title = 'r: {frame_along}') +
  transition_reveal(r)
animate(p, fps = 30, duration = 5)
## `geom_line()`: Each group consists of only one observation.

data_1973 <- Kandidat_long %>% filter(r == 1973)
partifarver <- c(
  "S" = "#E3000F",  
  "V" = "#00529F",            
  "FP" = "#FF7F00", 
  "KF" = "#1A932E",
  "CD" = "#7D3F98",
  "SF" = "#C32026",  
  "RV" = "#954FAD",     
  "KRF" = "#A67C52",
  "DKP" = "#AE0030",
  "DR" = "#B0B0B0"
)
ggplot(data_1973, aes(x = Parti, y = Mandater, fill = Parti)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", color = "black") +
  scale_fill_manual(values = partifarver) +
  labs(title = "Folketingsvalg 1973 - Mandatfordeling",
       x = "Parti", y = "Antal mandater") +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1))
